the Best
            

            "At this juncture, we all
should hope for the best."

            So concludes an especially
muddled editorial <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Feb. 25</TIMEX> in the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Wall Street Journal</ENAMEX> . The muddle was
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">understandable</ENAMEX>, given that the topic was on-again, off-again, on-again
