power. But that was when <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Lawrence Walsh</ENAMEX> was investigating <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">President</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Reagan</ENAMEX>. Now
